<item>
            <title>[LU-7999] Object &apos;uuids&apos; was freed at line 1895 after being freed by calling &apos;realloc&apos; at line 1892 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7999</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;TRACEBACK&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A condition which occurs, leading to the defect liblustreapi.c:1878: ret!=0 is false&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A condition which occurs, leading to the defect liblustreapi.c:1883: uuids== ( (void* )0) is false&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;An event which alters the program&apos;s state, leading to the defect liblustreapi.c:1892: &apos;uuids&apos; is freed by calling &apos;realloc&apos;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;An event which alters the program&apos;s state, leading to the defect liblustreapi.c:1895: &apos;uuids&apos; is double freed by calling &apos;free&apos;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
